{"tid":1529401,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[shining online] 防uv防曬帽","createTime":"2019-09-01T17:23:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-06T16:05:37.000Z","uid":313362,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"aafef039b55fa3e343077c25f8c698adfbe974d2","tid":1529401,"uid":313362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T17:23:47.000Z","msg":"平時行街見唔少巴絲冇做足防曬措施<br />\n就算有遮<span style=\"color: red;\">面</span>但好多都露哂對<span style=\"color: red;\">耳</span>出嚟<br />\n呢排雖然成日落雨<br />\n但都唔可以忽視陽光嘅威脅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家知唔知曬得多好易老架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有<span style=\"color: red;\">頭頂</span>都要遮住<br />\n如果唔係啲頭髮頭皮曬得多會甩頭髮變光頭架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n強烈要求以後人人有頂呢啲防曬帽<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ali-img.net/img.alicdn.com/imgextra/i4/699783941/O1CN01mljnq21ez1Qn6ZQEf_!!0-item_pic.jpg_v_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ali-img.net%2Fimg.alicdn.com%2Fimgextra%2Fi4%2F699783941%2FO1CN01mljnq21ez1Qn6ZQEf_%21%210-item_pic.jpg_v_600.jpg&h=5c644e1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">包頭遮面遮耳包都陷</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔想大家咁後生就成面斑禿哂頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50dba3b0b0de7ab5d4a20ea77530828034126050","tid":1529401,"uid":196699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T15:10:19.000Z","msg":"遮面塊布叫咩名"},{"pid":"fb9806fd32b96cd7cbae86727fddfa1f1b90d472","tid":1529401,"uid":313362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"50dba3b0b0de7ab5d4a20ea77530828034126050","tid":1529401,"uid":196699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T15:10:19.000Z","msg":"遮面塊布叫咩名"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T16:05:37.000Z","msg":"耳仔側邊位痴住頂帽嗰兩塊布有位可以啪埋遮臉塊布<br />\n正路會連住咁一齊賣<br />\n我都唔知叫咩"}]}